title: Escape From Hell Classic Full v1.3.3
description:
Escape From Hell The Adrenaline Horror Game is a dynamic and easy to control arcade game, offering quick play in the style of classic arcade games.
Take the challenge and pogo dance with the devil in the rhythm of the deepest depths of hell !!!

Escape From Hell is a true adrenaline horror. After steady beginning, the pace rapidly grows with every level, causing uncontrolled adrenaline rush, demanding constant focus and agility. But don't worry, training and perseverance are what it takes to pass all of them.

Your task is to dodge the evil zombies that get in your way and perfidiously try to interrupt your escape.

Luckily, time to time good faith grants you with power stars. If collected, stars by far boost your treasures, and therefore, your chances of climbing to the very top of the global ranking.

Features:

* easy to control
* swift action	
* eye-catching HD graphics
* excitatory soundtrack
* global ranking
